editorialSummary.text: Part of Wolfgang Puck's international steakhouse group, featuring a dining room and lounge.

originalText.text: I recently dined at this place, and it was an exceptional experience. The ambiance was elegant, the service was impeccable, and the steak was cooked to perfection. Every dish was bursting with flavor, and the presentation was top-notch. The staff was knowledgeable and attentive, ensuring a memorable dining experience. I highly recommend this place  for anyone looking for a superb steakhouse dining experience.

originalText.text: Had breakfast and dinner here while staying at the Four Seasons and we we’re not disappointed. The chicken and steak dishes were well prepared and the raw bar items were high quality. The only negative things we could find during dinner were that our server’s shift ended mid meal and the decanters that were showcased had not been cleaned and had fingerprints all over them; not a big deal but didn’t meet the standard they’re trying to set. Breakfast, however, was perfect. The eggs were top quality as was the fruit and the service was flawless. There’s plenty of options for restaurants in Manhattan but I would likely visit this location again.

originalText.text:
This exquisite fine dining establishment surpasses all expectations in every aspect. From the moment you step foot into the opulent premises, you are greeted with an air of elegance and sophistication. The culinary experience that unfolds is nothing short of extraordinary.

The selection of prime meats is unparalleled, sourced from only the finest suppliers and prepared with the utmost precision and skill. Each dish is a masterpiece, meticulously crafted to tantalize the senses and leave a lasting impression on even the most discerning palates.

The service provided by the highly trained and attentive staff is nothing short of impeccable. Every detail is meticulously executed, from the seamless coordination of courses to the discreet presence of the waitstaff, ensuring a flawless dining experience.

The pastry chef, Aura, deserves special mention for her exceptional creations. Her desserts are a symphony of flavors, artfully presented and expertly balanced. Each bite is a revelation, showcasing her remarkable talent and commitment to culinary excellence.

Furthermore, the management team's dedication to providing a luxurious and exclusive atmosphere is evident in every aspect of the restaurant. From the lavish interior design to the personalized attention given to each guest, no expense is spared in creating an ambiance of unparalleled luxury and refinement.

In conclusion, this establishment sets a new standard for fine dining experiences. It is a haven for those seeking the pinnacle of culinary artistry, impeccable service, and an unforgettable evening of indulgence. A visit to this restaurant is an absolute must for anyone with a discerning taste for luxury.

originalText.text:
The food at this place is great but I am mostly writing this review because I met a waitress there who has to be recognized publicly. I believe her name is Essence, but if you go there you will be able to spot who I am talking about because she looks like a young Naomi Campbell, absolutely gorgeous. She was prompt, smart, caring, and knowledgable about the food, everything she recommended was so delicious. She just had this friendly demeanor that made me and my friend all happy. By the end of our day, two of us said, "She's the best waitress we've ever had”, unfortunately her shift ended mid meal and as much as the rest of staff is nice, she was definitely above and beyond.
Food is also great. The roasted chicken with salsa verde is unbelievable. All side dishes, as well as the sliders and dessert are also 10/10. I’ll definitely come back!

originalText.text: Had dinner at Cut for a special occasion, then again for a drink at the bar on another visit to the area. The food, service, and atmosphere here were all fantastic both times. This restaurant is located within the Four Seasons hotel downtown, making it a nice go-to spot if you're staying at that property.
